You see it?

486
00:27:53,591 --> 00:27:55,509
Let's go, man. Close the door.

487
00:27:55,551 --> 00:27:56,969
All right, quit playing, Ray.

488
00:27:57,052 --> 00:27:59,513
We'll be in here a while.
Now go on now!

489
00:28:07,229 --> 00:28:08,272
Where you from, Ray?

490
00:28:08,355 --> 00:28:09,565
North Florida.

491
00:28:09,982 --> 00:28:11,484
Oh, North Florida boy.

492
00:28:12,026 --> 00:28:13,194
Your people still down there?

493
00:28:13,319 --> 00:28:14,487
No.

494
00:28:15,696 --> 00:28:16,822
All right.

495
00:28:17,323 --> 00:28:18,824
Hey, uh, pardon me for askin',

496
00:28:18,908 --> 00:28:20,826
but how do you 
get around so good ...

